



## Installed Packages

This project uses several Python packages to enhance its functionality. Key packages include:

- [Django](https://www.djangoproject.com/): The web framework for building the project.
- [Django Rest Framework](https://www.django-rest-framework.org/): A powerful and flexible toolkit for building Web APIs.
- [Django Rest Framework Simple JWT](https://django-rest-framework-simplejwt.readthedocs.io/en/latest/): A simple JWT authentication for Django Rest Framework.

