## Project Structure

- `app/`: Contains the main Django app.
- `project/`: Contains the project settings and configuration.
- `templates/`: Stores HTML templates.
- `static/`: Stores static files (CSS, JavaScript, images, etc.).
- `media/`: Stores media files (uploaded user content).
- `requirements.txt`: Lists project dependencies.
- `manage.py`: Django management script.

## URLs Configuration

The project's URL configuration is defined in `project/urls.py`. Here are some of the main URLs:

- `/`: Home page.
- `/contact-us/`: Contact page.
- `/api/get-jwt-token/`: Generates a JWT token.
- `/api/token/`: Generates a JWT token (using `TokenObtainPairView` from `rest_framework_simplejwt`).
- `/signup/`: User registration page.
- `/login/`: Built-in login view.
- `/logout/`: Logs the user out and redirects to the home page.
- `/accounts/profile/`: User profile page.

